elements of `K`, which we decompose as `c_0 + c_1 · α + … + c_{14} · α^14`.
The combined form is `f = f_0 + α · f_1 + … + α^14 · f_{14}`, with each
`f_j` a level-1 weight-184 form with rational coefficients in `(E₄, E₆)`.

